  "general_provisions": "This bill addresses notification of usage of water by end users.",
  "hilighted_provisions": "This bill:<hr><ltbullet>defines terms;<hr><ltbullet>grants rulemaking authority;<hr><ltbullet>requires a retail water supplier to provide certain notifications regarding water usage;<hr><ltbullet>requires a secondary water supplier to provide certain notifications regarding water usage, with exceptions;<hr><ltbullet>directs rulemaking;<hr><ltbullet>provides for the method of notification; and<hr><ltbullet>addresses liability.",
